{"tid":2147600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"難得外國咁幫我地 我地要回應 走番出黎抗爭","createTime":"2020-08-09T10:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T12:29:05.000Z","uid":105995,"like":66,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a85501abf693ac170305c21408f3c1f1e19d66","tid":2147600,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"我地一定要有回應 先可以鼓勵美國政府 外國社會 繼續幫我地 <br />\n<br />\n人始終有惰性 要有互動先可以炒熱個氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得勢頭咁好 你都唔想佢地奶番共架<br />\n<br />\n宜家嘅回應完全唔夠呀！我覺得以下幾樣野請各位盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 快閃文宣: 貼紙/有字冇字memo/巴士... 快閃安全地做，最緊要快同多，内容反而其次，炒熱本地氣氛<br />\n<br />\n2. Airdrop: 相對安全，可盡做<br />\n<br />\n3. 國際戰線: twitter/facebook... 平時做多d<br />\n<br />\n4. 遊行/集會: 我覺得要短期內搞番反國安法主題嘅集會/和理shop/和理sing 都好，可以俾外國報導，俾佢地知道我地未放棄，請繼續幫香港，當然要文宣配合<br />\n<br />\n5. 海外: 流亡海外兄弟應開始籌建海外組織，係未來凝聚connect移民流亡香港人，海外繼續抗共"},{"pid":"6d497170ef39321a6673756eabf13dc43fe8ed03","tid":2147600,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6c7dadf35644eb837c9f0805d0b1c75b819fea","tid":2147600,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d2924dd15d11ea8d1c1faa595963106bd0a176","tid":2147600,"uid":105995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"6. 連登推行動post, 假膠五毛分化post由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n7. 平時繼續鼓勵更多人抗爭 努力share中共嘅衰嘢"},{"pid":"4f55354b08bc9ec476e41af8f488291ff3412f6a","tid":2147600,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb85af238761694de1d16bb8d3fe8cc530fc011","tid":2147600,"uid":105995